{"tid":1651382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"客貨車運載疑似警員做法好有問題","createTime":"2019-10-13T10:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T04:44:51.000Z","uid":103981,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5b59fc3523c43d1c211678a8b060714c0f8a1d3c","tid":1651382,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:27:57.000Z","msg":"成班友又唔出示委任證，又無編號，隨時係架不知名客貨車走落黎，擎槍威嚇公眾，其實對公共安全構成極大威脅。<br />\n假若有日，有不法分子租到警察戲服，再租架車，配把真槍，係街上為非作歹，咁就大鑊了。<br />\n<br />\n當然，有人可能話警方有行動需要。但警察而家唔係有特定對象要捉，唔係要防止對方識別到佢地身份。佢地行為只為驅散市民，根本無需要咁樣做。<br />\n請問有無立法會代議事可以就此入稟法庭，禁制警方呢種行動方式？另外，亦應就每宗無手令、無特定/拘捕對象情況下闖入私人物業、每宗無人情況下發射催淚彈既情況作司法覆核？"},{"pid":"3c7a0657300e58c1af8557268a233f3b5910b31b","tid":1651382,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"警要新仔幫上頭及大陸武警嘅罪行頂罪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651133\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651133</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5884040c130fb91c9858600a6a353b40ba16af7e","tid":1651382,"uid":63952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:33:24.000Z","msg":"用火魔法嘅話佢坐靈車嚟都冇撚所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc572eee2cbf148dff22c2230b09cae596be03d0","tid":1651382,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:34:29.000Z","msg":"成班議員唔做野"},{"pid":"f0320849d21d6cfce2aa9359dc7b1f7894116002","tid":1651382,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5884040c130fb91c9858600a6a353b40ba16af7e","tid":1651382,"uid":63952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:33:24.000Z","msg":"用火魔法嘅話佢坐靈車嚟都冇撚所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8b7926b1d9d5ef772125bdd44e3ccf197c1652","tid":1651382,"uid":67903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":